WEBVTT

00:01:56.040 --> 00:02:02.120
And the key to understanding
this dark universe is gravity.

00:02:03.760 --> 00:02:07.456
So 1500 million years ago,

00:02:07.480 --> 00:02:15.070
many galaxies away from the earth,
two black holes were for years dancing

00:02:15.400 --> 00:02:18.200
and slowly came close to each other

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:23.016
and finally almost at the speed of light

00:02:23.040 --> 00:02:29.016
they collided and this collision
led to a big black hole.

00:02:29.040 --> 00:02:33.336
This black hole was about the size
of our Rajasthan,